The,Seldon,REST,API,allows,developers,to,programmatically,interact,with,the,platform,s,items,users,and,actions,in,order,to,generate,recommendations,The,Seldon,predictive,platform,uses,structured,historical,data,to,generate,recommendations,for,different,kinds,of,items,e,g,music,movies,articles,It,produces,these,recommendations,using,a,variety,of,algorithms,and,can,create,reports,containing,an,assortment,of,statistics